title: Symbol
content:
Symbol may refer to:

  • Ancient symbol, obtained from cleaning uncleaned finds.
  • Enchanted symbol, used during the Mage Arena II miniquest.
  • Goblin symbol book, a book containing symbols of the twelve goblin tribes.
  • Hallowed symbol, an item purchased from the Hallowed Sepulchre.
  • Holy symbol, a blessed symbol of Saradomin.
    • Unstrung symbol, the item's unstrung variant.
    • Unblessed symbol, the item's unblessed variant.
  • Holy symbol (Icthlarin's Little Helper), an item obtained during Icthlarin's Little Helper.
  • Old symbol, obtained from cleaning uncleaned finds.
  • Unholy symbol, a blessed symbol of Zamorak.
    • Unstrung emblem, the item's unstrung variant.
    • Unpowered symbol, the item's unblessed variant.
  • Unholy symbol (Icthlarin's Little Helper), an item obtained during Icthlarin's Little Helper.
  • Icon space furniture:
    • Guthix symbol
    • Saradomin symbol
    • Zamorak symbol
  • Symbol (big book of bangs), interface items found in the big book of bangs.
 This page is used to distinguish between articles with similar names.
